OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,FSark Electricity's boss has sent a
OL,7,Fletter to all customers stating that
OL,8,Fthey will start paying a legal levy on
OL,9,Ftheir bills from Monday 1 September.
OL,11,FIt comes after Sark's Government,
OL,12,FChief Pleas, voted to compulsorily
OL,13,Fpurchase the company.
OL,15,FHowever, Alan Witney-Price, the sole
OL,16,FDirector of Sark Electricity Limited,
OL,17,Fpreviously said he has "no desire to
OL,18,Fsell to the Chief Pleas" over concerns
OL,19,Fabout how they will run the utility.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/15
