OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,FHe claims he must now raise #500,000
OL,7,Fto fight the move in court, funded
OL,8,Fthrough an extra 40p per unit charge
OL,9,Fon Sark residents' bills.
OL,11,FMoney from the levy will be held in a
OL,12,Ffund by the advocates, with any
OL,13,Fremaining funds being returned to
OL,14,Fcustomers.
OL,16,FHowever, the move could make the
OL,17,Fpeople of Sark pay for some of the
OL,18,Fmost expensive electricity in the
OL,19,Fworld.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/15
