OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,FA release from Sark Electricity
OL,7,FLimited (SEL) states: "SEL is now
OL,8,Fforced into a situation where the
OL,9,FCompany must mount a legal challenge
OL,10,Fagainst Chief Pleas' move to seize its
OL,11,Fassets and remove its income stream.
OL,13,F"Chief Pleas has publicly stated that
OL,14,Fit expects to pay significantly less
OL,15,Fthan the market value already agreed
OL,16,Ffor the Company; this matter is both
OL,17,Fserious and urgent. Legal challenges
OL,18,Fcannot be delayed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
