CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1756324673
OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,F"The costs for both sides are paid by
OL,7,Fresidents, and money that would be
OL,8,Fbetter invested into the grid and into
OL,9,Flocal services such as improving
OL,10,Ftourism or providing healthcare
OL,11,Fsubsidies, instead goes to expensive
OL,12,FAdvocates.
OL,14,F"The Company has done everything that
OL,15,Fit could to avoid increasing the cost
OL,16,Fof electricity at this time. However,
OL,17,Fit must fund its defence against the
OL,18,FChief Pleas' move to seize its assets
OL,19,Fagainst its will.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
