CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1756324673
OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,F"Like you, we look forward to the day
OL,7,Fwhen the legal levy can be removed
OL,8,Fonce again and Sark residents can
OL,9,Fenjoy the cheapest electricity
OL,10,Favailable for the jurisdiction."
OL,12,FThe company claims it can charge
OL,13,F"whatever it wishes" for electricity
OL,14,Fsince the previous control order
OL,15,Fexpired in March 2025.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/15
