OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,FHowever, Chief Pleas stated: "It is
OL,7,Ffor the Electricity Price Control
OL,8,FCommissioner, after investigation, to
OL,9,Fdetermine, under The Control of
OL,10,FElectricity Prices (Sark) Law, 2016,
OL,11,Fif the prices charged by SEL are fair
OL,12,Fand reasonable.
OL,14,F"If the Electricity Price Control
OL,15,FCommissioner determines the prices are
OL,16,Fnot fair and reasonable, he has the
OL,17,Fpower to introduce a price control
OL,18,Forder."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/15
