OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,FAlan Witney-Price was scathing in his
OL,7,Fcriticism of Sark Electricity, saying
OL,8,Fthey have not engaged with the company
OL,9,Ffor five years, and that they are
OL,10,Funable to get on with infrastructure
OL,11,Fprojects.
OL,13,FMr Witney-Price says: "It's the
OL,14,Fcompany's legal fight with Chief
OL,15,FPleas, it is not my legal fight with
OL,16,FChief Pleas and under company law, the
OL,17,Fcompany has an obligation to protect
OL,18,Fits assets and ensure that it remains
OL,19,Fsolvent.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
