PN,38308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1756324673
OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,F"I sold the company. It was an
OL,7,Fexcellent deal for them, which came at
OL,8,Fno cost to Sark, no cost to residents
OL,9,Fbeyond maintaining the electricity
OL,10,Fsupply, and would have reduced the
OL,11,Fprice significantly. The Chief Pleas
OL,12,Finterfered with that existing sale.
OL,14,F"It's an absolute failure of good
OL,15,Fgovernance. It's an absolute failure
OL,16,Fof process."
OL,18,FMr Witney-Price also says that if
OL,19,Fcustomers don't pay the legal levy,
OL,20,Fthen they will be moved on to a pay
OL,21,Fmeter.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
