OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1756324673
OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,FHe explains: "We have no intention
OL,7,Fwhatsoever to put the people of Sark
OL,8,Funder something they don't need to be
OL,9,Fput under, but the reality is this is
OL,10,Fa political problem, not an
OL,11,Felectricity problem.
OL,13,F"If the people of Sark want somebody
OL,14,Fto complain to, it should be Chief
OL,15,FPleas. They've created the crisis, and
OL,16,Fthey keep refusing permission to lay
OL,17,Fcables and to change infrastructure.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1756324673
OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,F"This needs a judicial review. The
OL,7,Fcourts need to see if the Chief Pleas
OL,8,Fhave followed good governance, and if
OL,9,Fthey have and found that I'm wrong,
OL,10,Fthen clearly the fund will have to be
OL,11,Freimbursed.
OL,13,F"Give us permission to do the work and
OL,14,Fsell the company, or see us in court
OL,15,Funder a judicial review. I think
OL,16,Fdialogue is the best way forward. But
OL,17,Ffor five years, they've refused,
OL,18,Fbecause they know they're in the wrong.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
