PN,38311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1756324673
OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,F"Sark Electricity is not abusing the
OL,7,Fcustomer; it is doing everything in
OL,8,Fits power to support them."
OL,10,FPaul Armorgie, a resident of Sark and
OL,11,Fhotel director, described the move
OL,12,Ffrom the Sark Electricity boss as
OL,13,F"outrageous".
OL,15,FHe explains: "It's been slapped on us
OL,16,Fwith literally no notice at all. It
OL,17,Feffectively doubles our electricity
OL,18,Fbill with a week's notice, which is
OL,19,Fjust outrageous.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1756324673
OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,F"Most of the people I'm talking to are
OL,7,Fsaying they are very happy to pay
OL,8,Ftheir electricity bill, but they will
OL,9,Fnot be paying the legal surcharge
OL,10,Fthat's been slapped on us.
OL,12,F"Hopefully, it'll be a very short-
OL,13,Flived exercise, and hopefully the
OL,14,Fcompulsory purchase will go through
OL,15,Fwithin the next few weeks.
OL,17,F"There's undoubtedly a dispute between
OL,18,Fthe owner of the power station and
OL,19,FChief Pleas, but that's got to be
OL,20,Fresolved for the sake of the consumers
OL,21,Fon Sark."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
