OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,FDespite the price hike and threat of
OL,7,Flegal action, the Chief Pleas believe
OL,8,Fthat the issue will blow over fairly
OL,9,Fshortly.
OL,11,FConseiller Mike Locke, Chair of the
OL,12,FFuture Energy Committee, explains:
OL,13,F"This is not unsurprising from the
OL,14,Fsource concerned. I think everybody's
OL,15,Fpretty tired of these arbitrary price
OL,16,Frises and reactions from SEL, so this
OL,17,Fis just another one we have to
OL,18,Fnavigate.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1756324673
OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,F"The Price Commissioner has launched
OL,7,Fan investigation into this.
OL,8,FElectricity prices as a regulated
OL,9,Findustry on Sark are an entirely
OL,10,Fmatter for the Commissioner and SEL.
OL,11,FWe look forward to his determination
OL,12,Fas quickly as possible."
OL,14,FConseiller John Gill, head of the
OL,15,FPolicy and Finance Committee, also
OL,16,Ftold ITV News: "I think this price
OL,17,Frise will likely be resolved once the
OL,18,FElectricity Price Control Commissioner
OL,19,Fhas been able to do a thorough
OL,20,Finvestigation to see whether it's fair
OL,21,For justified.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F383A1756324673
OL,3,CElectricity boss hikes prices to fund
OL,4,Clegal fees against government
OL,6,F"Ultimately, the situation with the
OL,7,Felectricity company is going to be
OL,8,Fbrought to a conclusion when we
OL,9,Fcomplete the compulsory purchase and
OL,10,Fthe company is in the island's own
OL,11,Fhands.
OL,13,F"Anybody will be shocked to receive a
OL,14,Fletter in the last week of August,
OL,15,Ftelling you that electricity costs are
OL,16,Fgoing to double in September. I can't
OL,17,Fthink of any business operating
OL,18,Fanywhere else in the world that we
OL,19,Fthink it was okay to give everybody a
OL,20,Fsurprise like that at the end of
OL,21,FAugust."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
